<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .header { background: #f59e0b; color: white; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 40px 20px; background: #ffffff; }
    .alert-box { background: #fef3c7; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .code { background: #1f2937; color: #10b981; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; font-family: monospace; overflow-x: auto; margin: 10px 0; }
    .footer { padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; background: #f9fafb; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>üö® Database Backup Alert</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Backup Failed</h2>
      
      <div class="alert-box">
        <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{timestamp}}</p>
        <p><strong>Database:</strong> {{databaseName}}</p>
        <p><strong>Status:</strong> FAILED</p>
      </div>

      <p><strong>Error Details:</strong></p>
      <div class="code">{{errorMessage}}</div>

      <p><strong>Recommended Actions:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Check database connectivity</li>
        <li>Verify backup directory permissions</li>
        <li>Ensure sufficient disk space</li>
        <li>Review database logs</li>
      </ul>

      <p style="color: #dc2626; font-weight: bold;">‚ö†Ô∏è Immediate action required to prevent data loss!</p>
      
      <p>Please investigate this issue as soon as possible. If the problem persists, contact your system administrator.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} {{platformName}} - System Administrator</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
